  description:
    English: "Farmer Monkey is a calm and hardworking monkey who believes that steady
      effort always wins in the long run \U0001F33E\n\nHe may not look powerful at
      first, but his true strength lies in patience and productivity. While others
      focus on fighting, Farmer Monkey focuses on growth. Over time, he generates
      valuable resources for the team, helping you deploy stronger units and control
      the battlefield."
    Vietnamese: "Kh\u1EC9 N\xF4ng D\xE2n l\xE0 m\u1ED9t ch\xFA kh\u1EC9 \u0111i\u1EC1m
      t\u0129nh v\xE0 ch\u0103m ch\u1EC9, tin r\u1EB1ng n\u1ED7 l\u1EF1c b\u1EC1n
      b\u1EC9 lu\xF4n mang l\u1EA1i chi\u1EBFn th\u1EAFng v\u1EC1 l\xE2u d\xE0i \U0001F33E\r\n\r\nTho\u1EA1t
      nh\xECn c\xF3 v\u1EBB kh\xF4ng m\u1EA1nh m\u1EBD, nh\u01B0ng s\u1EE9c m\u1EA1nh
      th\u1EF1c s\u1EF1 c\u1EE7a ch\xFA n\u1EB1m \u1EDF s\u1EF1 ki\xEAn nh\u1EABn
      v\xE0 n\u0103ng su\u1EA5t. Trong khi nh\u1EEFng ch\xFA kh\u1EC9 kh\xE1c t\u1EADp
      trung v\xE0o chi\u1EBFn \u0111\u1EA5u, Kh\u1EC9 N\xF4ng D\xE2n l\u1EA1i t\u1EADp
      trung v\xE0o s\u1EF1 ph\xE1t tri\u1EC3n. Theo th\u1EDDi gian, ch\xFA t\u1EA1o
      ra nh\u1EEFng ngu\u1ED3n l\u1EF1c qu\xFD gi\xE1 cho \u0111\u1ED9i, gi\xFAp
      b\u1EA1n tri\u1EC3n khai c\xE1c \u0111\u01A1n v\u1ECB m\u1EA1nh m\u1EBD h\u01A1n
      v\xE0 ki\u1EC3m so\xE1t chi\u1EBFn tr\u01B0\u1EDDng."
